  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  patients with heart function of NYHAⅠ-Ⅲ degree

          -  patients would like to accept the follow-up and sign the informed consent

          -  patients who have the breast surgery for the frist time

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  pregnant or nursing women

          -  combined with coronary artery disease

          -  patients with heart function of NYHAⅣdegree

          -  enrollment in other clinical trials at the same time not reaching the primary endpoint
             and probably interference the present trial
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
